      },
      "date": "2013-01-22 21:38:51.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: I would prefer that you didn't submit this\n\nI think this would be acceptable, but I it would be better if the test is only skipped if the MDS supports the layout_lock feature:\n\ntest_40() {\n        # always need connection to MDS to verify layout during IO. LU-2628\n        lctl get_param mdc.*.connect_flags | grep -q layout_lock &&\n                skip \"layout_lock needs MDS connection for IO\" && return 0\n\n(PS - please remember tabs for indentation in this function)",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 1
    },
