      "date": "2013-01-26 10:30:05.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 3: Verified\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.3/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/80dcd378-67a1-11e2-9eee-52540035b04c).  Ran 12 tests.  No failures.",
